These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, scrabble, canasta
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, 7up, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, rock-climbing, baking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, april, january
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing canasta##2
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta   | backgammon  | scrabble  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | tea    | almond-milk      | 7up    |
| Hobby   | baking | video-games | rock-climbing | hiking |
| Birthday     | january  | june       | july    | april     |

