.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, cucumber, eggplant, pear
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, october, march
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, brown, blood-red, coral
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bolivar, game, old-henry
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes coral is the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who likes blood-red and the dunhill-smoker##2
6. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who likes coral##2
7. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food         | pear | cucumber    | eggplant  | lime    |
| Birthday   | december      | august  | march  | october |
| Color           | coral      | blood-red       | brown      | green       |
| Cigar         | bolivar    | old-henry | game | dunhill |

