4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the fan punk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the fan r&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the fan trance is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in december##2
9. the person who's birthday is in march is between the fan punk and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre        | classical | punk     | trance   | r&b     |
