The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, iris, marigold, aconite
There are 4 different nationalities: german, british, dutch, french
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, blue, coral, red
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 5. the french is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the french##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who growsiris is the british##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who likes red and the german##2
10. the dutch is the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby          | chess         | traveling         | skydiving     | photography      |
| Flower           | marigold | aconite | balloon-flower    | iris     |
